     1Рєњ# TS-Pattern v3 to v4 Migration Guide
     3Рєњ## Breaking changes
     5Рєњ### Imports
     7Рєњtype-specific wildcard patterns have moved from `__.<pattern>` to a new `Pattern` qualified module, also exported as `P` by ts-pattern.
     8Рєњ
     9Рєњ```diff
    10Рєњ- import { match, __ } from 'ts-pattern';
    11Рєњ+ import { match, Pattern } from 'ts-pattern';
    12Рєњ
    13Рєњ
    14Рєњconst toString = (value: string | number) =>
    15Рєњ  match(value)
    16Рєњ-   .with(__.string, (v) => v)
    17Рєњ-   .with(__.number, (v) => `${v}`)
    18Рєњ+   .with(Pattern.string, (v) => v)
    19Рєњ+   .with(Pattern.number, (v) => `${v}`)
    20Рєњ    .exhaustive();
    21Рєњ```
    22Рєњ
    23Рєњor
    24Рєњ
    25Рєњ```diff
      РєњРђд
    39Рєњ#### `__` Рђд
    57Рєњ#### `select()`, `not()`, `when()` Рђд
    79Рєњ#### `Pattern` type Рђд
